  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An error occurred for some reason, and the error mixed the games.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2683360/extras/20e4ea4548bf779f4a7007d9ea01bff3.avif?t=1747744152\" width=192 height=108 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2683360/extras/49a5c5d0dcce11952abc71b8c3e6cc19.avif?t=1747744152\" width=192 height=108 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2683360/extras/61905fb56e0f69c558d9b36f57c04558.avif?t=1747744152\" width=192 height=108 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2683360/extras/db8c511cd70483096e2c77d31493ac84.avif?t=1747744152\" width=192 height=108 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To resolve this error, the adaptive error correction program \"Error_Boy\" appears.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Error_Boy\" is an adaptive error correction program that uses items or weapons extracted from games.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Debug\" your enemies with a variety of items, weapons, and upgrades!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >@Medieval Voyager</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Medieval Voyager is a medieval fantasy game with black and white colors.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2683360/extras/a1951e4c7ffffcdd7b7d2a1defecda03.poster.avif?t=1747744152\" width=600 height=338